window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This damn power is a curse.</b></p> <p>I've taken everything from the wolves. Their magic. Their pride.</p> <p>Their alphas. </p> <p>But now I wish I could give it all back. Fulfilling my role as the Moon Guardian has brought a new force to this world, one that might even be worse than the wolves.</p> <p>If that's even possible. </p> <p>The realms are merging and with it come threats we thought were dead. Hunters. Panthers. Supernaturals who all want a bite of humanity because we're one of the few realms who have any left. </p> <p>I need to protect my family. I need to protect them by any means necessary. </p> <p>Even if it means taking the time to understand my alphas. I don't know if I can ever forgive them, but perhaps I can listen to what they have to say. </p> <p>They will grovel. </p> <p>They will beg. </p> <p>And in the end, they will follow my lead, or I'll let their magic die with me.</p> <p><i>Moon Cursed </i>is book two in a reverse-harem rejected-mate series. There will be an HEA and second-chance tropes where her alphas will grovel at her feet for ever daring to reject her as their mate.</p>"; 
